endpoints.description:
Log a health entry (like morning loop).

Example:
{
    "metrics": [
        {
            "metric_type": "lab_result",
            "metric_name": "blood_glucose",
            "value": 20.8,
            "unit": "mmol/L"
        },
        {
            "metric_type": "medication",
            "metric_name": "Degludec",
            "value": 11,
            "unit": "units"
        }
    ],
    "entry_type": "routine",
    "condition_name": "Type 1 Diabetes",
    "notes": "Morning loop"
}
